&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are looking for a meticulous SDET who will be responsible for the design and implementation of automated tests and test environments for Arcana. The engineer must have a passion for diving into data and technology, be a problem solver, and have a desire to improve software quality within a team environment. This role is critical in ensuring technology functions efficiently and effectively, minimizes errors, and helps meet software quality goals.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/div&gt;
