&lt;p&gt;- Tool call design: schema design that LLMs actually follow reliably across providers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Evaluation &amp;amp; Harness&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
