&lt;p&gt;- You&#39;ve written eval harnesses from scratch and you have opinions about what makes a ground truth dataset actually useful&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- You&#39;ve debugged LLM non-determinism in production and built systems resilient to it&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- You&#39;ve worked with streaming LLM responses and built infrastructure around partial output handling&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weaker signal (but not disqualifying):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
